room_title: Escape room "Sleeping Spirits" by Gotham Escape Room in Philadelphia
room_description: A famous paranormal skeptic has gone missing within the Dolphin Hotel. He has visited haunted locations all over the world, but he has never been gone this long before. Horrific stories of death surround this place and spirits have been known to linger in the hotel’s rooms. You must find this skeptic and escape from the Dolphin Hotel before you are forced to “check out” permanently.
